{"chapters": {"overview": ["<div class=\"slide cover\"><div class=\"wordmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span><span class=\"name\">Minuto<b>Real</b></span></div><div class=\"kicker\">O CURSO OFICIAL</div><h1><span class=\"lt\">BLENDER</span> <span class=\"bd\">FUNDAMENTALS</span></h1><div class=\"author\">por Blender Foundation</div><div class=\"hook\"><span class=\"num\">4</span><span class=\"lbl\">ideias<br>que <span>ficam</span></span></div><div class=\"swipe\"><span>arrasta</span><span class=\"arrow\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M12 32h36M34 18l16 14-16 14\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"4\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide concept\"><div class=\"topbar\"><span class=\"brandmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span>Minuto<b>Real</b></span></div><div class=\"ed\"><div class=\"ed-head\"><div class=\"ed-num\">1</div><div class=\"ed-meta\"><div class=\"ed-kicker\">BLENDER FUNDAMENTALS</div><div class=\"ed-rule\"></div><div class=\"ed-source\"></div></div></div><h1 class=\"ed-title\">O workflow de produção</h1><p class=\"ed-body\"><span class=\"dc\">A</span> ordem oficial: <strong>Modelagem → Texturização → Shading → Rigging → Animação → Iluminação → Render → Compositing.</strong> Cada Workspace do Blender…</p><div class=\"ed-tip\"><span class=\"tipic\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M34 8L18 36h12l-4 20 20-30H34l4-18z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><div class=\"tiptext\"><div class=\"tiplabel\">Modelo mental</div><div class=\"tipbody\">produção é linha de montagem; pule etapa e retrabalha.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide concept\"><div class=\"topbar\"><span class=\"brandmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span>Minuto<b>Real</b></span></div><div class=\"ed\"><div class=\"ed-head\"><div class=\"ed-num\">2</div><div class=\"ed-meta\"><div class=\"ed-kicker\">BLENDER FUNDAMENTALS</div><div class=\"ed-rule\"></div><div class=\"ed-source\"></div></div></div><h1 class=\"ed-title\">F3 é a rota de fuga</h1><p class=\"ed-body\"><span class=\"dc\">N</span>ão decore menus: <strong>aperte F3 e busque o comando pelo nome</strong> ('bevel', 'shade smooth'). É o atalho que destrava qualquer função quando você sabe o…</p><div class=\"ed-tip\"><span class=\"tipic\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M34 8L18 36h12l-4 20 20-30H34l4-18z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><div class=\"tiptext\"><div class=\"tiplabel\">Produtividade</div><div class=\"tipbody\">F3 > caçar em submenu.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide concept\"><div class=\"topbar\"><span class=\"brandmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span>Minuto<b>Real</b></span></div><div class=\"ed\"><div class=\"ed-head\"><div class=\"ed-num\">3</div><div class=\"ed-meta\"><div class=\"ed-kicker\">BLENDER FUNDAMENTALS</div><div class=\"ed-rule\"></div><div class=\"ed-source\"></div></div></div><h1 class=\"ed-title\">Cycles × EEVEE</h1><p class=\"ed-body\"><strong><span class=\"dc\">C</span>ycles</strong> = path tracer físico (lento, foto-realista). <strong>EEVEE</strong> = tempo real (rápido, ótimo p/ preview e estilizado).</p><div class=\"ed-tip\"><span class=\"tipic\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M34 8L18 36h12l-4 20 20-30H34l4-18z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><div class=\"tiptext\"><div class=\"tiplabel\">Regra</div><div class=\"tipbody\">EEVEE p/ iterar/preview; Cycles p/ a entrega final.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide concept warn\"><div class=\"topbar\"><span class=\"brandmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span>Minuto<b>Real</b></span></div><div class=\"ed\"><div class=\"ed-head\"><div class=\"ed-num\">4</div><div class=\"ed-meta\"><div class=\"ed-kicker\">BLENDER FUNDAMENTALS</div><div class=\"ed-rule\"></div><div class=\"ed-source\"></div></div></div><h1 class=\"ed-title\">Nunca renderize direto p/ .mp4</h1><p class=\"ed-body\"><span class=\"dc\">A</span> prática oficial: <strong>renderize a animação para uma SEQUÊNCIA de imagens (PNG/EXR), nunca direto para .mp4.</strong> Um crash no meio invalida o vídeo…</p><div class=\"ed-tip\"><span class=\"tipic\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 8l20 8v13c0 14-9 23-20 27-11-4-20-13-20-27V16z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><div class=\"tiptext\"><div class=\"tiplabel\">Depois</div><div class=\"tipbody\">monte o filme no Video Sequencer (com áudio).</div></div></div></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide cta\"><div class=\"ghost\" style=\"bottom:150px;right:40px;font-size:300px\">+</div><div class=\"big\">Gostou?<br><span class=\"lt\">tem mais.</span></div><div class=\"rows\"><div class=\"row\"><span class=\"rico\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M14 12h36v40H14z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M14 24h36M14 38h36M24 12v12M40 24v14\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/></svg></span><p>O livro inteiro em 1 página: cheat sheet + PDF no <strong>acervo</strong> &mdash; link na bio.</p></div><div class=\"row\"><span class=\"rico\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><circle cx=\"32\" cy=\"32\" r=\"22\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/><path d=\"M27 23l16 9-16 9z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><p>Prefere assistir? Resumo de ~5 min no <strong>YouTube</strong>.</p></div><div class=\"row\"><span class=\"rico\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M34 8L18 36h12l-4 20 20-30H34l4-18z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><p>Um grande livro destilado por semana. <strong>Siga @minutoreal1701</strong>.</p></div></div><div class=\"save\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M18 10h28v44L32 44 18 54z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg>Salve para revisar</div><div class=\"handle\">@minutoreal1701</div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i></div></div>"], "ch01-primeiros-passos": ["<div class=\"slide cover\"><div class=\"wordmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span><span class=\"name\">Minuto<b>Real</b></span></div><div class=\"kicker\">CAPÍTULO 1 DE 3</div><h1><span class=\"lt\">BLENDER</span> <span class=\"bd\">FUNDAMENTALS</span></h1><div class=\"author\">por Blender Foundation</div><div class=\"hook\"><span class=\"num\">3</span><span class=\"lbl\">ideias<br>que <span>ficam</span></span></div><div class=\"swipe\"><span>arrasta</span><span class=\"arrow\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M12 32h36M34 18l16 14-16 14\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"4\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide concept\"><div class=\"topbar\"><span class=\"brandmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span>Minuto<b>Real</b></span></div><div class=\"ed\"><div class=\"ed-head\"><div class=\"ed-num\">1</div><div class=\"ed-meta\"><div class=\"ed-kicker\">BLENDER FUNDAMENTALS</div><div class=\"ed-rule\"></div><div class=\"ed-source\">Capítulo 1 &middot; <b>Primeiros Passos e Atalhos</b></div></div></div><h1 class=\"ed-title\">Os atalhos essenciais</h1><p class=\"ed-body\"><strong><span class=\"dc\">G</span> mover, R rotacionar, S escalar — adicione X/Y/Z para travar no eixo.</strong> TAB troca de modo; A seleciona tudo; B/C são box/circle select. Esses poucos atalhos cobrem 80% do trabalho.</p><div class=\"ed-tip\"><span class=\"tipic\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M34 8L18 36h12l-4 20 20-30H34l4-18z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><div class=\"tiptext\"><div class=\"tiplabel\">Confirme com Enter, cancele com Esc</div><div class=\"tipbody\">durante o transform.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide concept\"><div class=\"topbar\"><span class=\"brandmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span>Minuto<b>Real</b></span></div><div class=\"ed\"><div class=\"ed-head\"><div class=\"ed-num\">2</div><div class=\"ed-meta\"><div class=\"ed-kicker\">BLENDER FUNDAMENTALS</div><div class=\"ed-rule\"></div><div class=\"ed-source\">Capítulo 1 &middot; <b>Primeiros Passos e Atalhos</b></div></div></div><h1 class=\"ed-title\">Navegação e vistas</h1><p class=\"ed-body\"><span class=\"dc\">S</span>croll = zoom; <strong>Numpad 1/3/7 = frente/lado/topo; 5 = orto↔perspectiva; 0 = câmera ativa.</strong> O pie menu (~) dá acesso rápido às vistas e ao shading.</p><div class=\"ed-tip\"><span class=\"tipic\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M34 8L18 36h12l-4 20 20-30H34l4-18z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><div class=\"tiptext\"><div class=\"tiplabel\">Vistas ortográficas</div><div class=\"tipbody\">são essenciais para modelar com precisão.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide concept\"><div class=\"topbar\"><span class=\"brandmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span>Minuto<b>Real</b></span></div><div class=\"ed\"><div class=\"ed-head\"><div class=\"ed-num\">3</div><div class=\"ed-meta\"><div class=\"ed-kicker\">BLENDER FUNDAMENTALS</div><div class=\"ed-rule\"></div><div class=\"ed-source\">Capítulo 1 &middot; <b>Primeiros Passos e Atalhos</b></div></div></div><h1 class=\"ed-title\">Collections e Workspaces</h1><p class=\"ed-body\"><strong><span class=\"dc\">U</span>se Collections (M) para agrupar objetos e Workspaces para cada etapa</strong> (Layout, Modeling, Shading, Render...). Nomeie tudo desde o início — cena organizada é cena que escala.</p><div class=\"ed-tip\"><span class=\"tipic\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M34 8L18 36h12l-4 20 20-30H34l4-18z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><div class=\"tiptext\"><div class=\"tiplabel\">Hábito oficial</div><div class=\"tipbody\">nada de 'Cube.001, Cube.002' largados na cena.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide lessons\"><div class=\"topbar\"><span class=\"brandmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span>Minuto<b>Real</b></span></div><div class=\"ed\"><div class=\"ed-head\"><div class=\"ed-num\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M18 10h28v44L32 44 18 54z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></div><div class=\"ed-meta\"><div class=\"ed-kicker\">BLENDERFUNDAMENTALS</div><div class=\"ed-rule\"></div><div class=\"ed-source\">Capítulo 1 &middot; <b>Primeiros Passos e Atalhos</b></div></div></div><h1 class=\"ed-title\">Lições-Chave do Capítulo 1</h1><ul class=\"lessons-list\"><li><span class=\"lnum\">1</span>G/R/S (+X/Y/Z) e TAB cobrem a maior parte do trabalho.</li><li><span class=\"lnum\">2</span>Numpad para vistas ortográficas e câmera é essencial.</li><li><span class=\"lnum\">3</span>Collections + Workspaces mantêm a cena organizada e escalável.</li></ul></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide cta\"><div class=\"ghost\" style=\"bottom:150px;right:40px;font-size:300px\">+</div><div class=\"big\">Gostou?<br><span class=\"lt\">tem mais.</span></div><div class=\"rows\"><div class=\"row\"><span class=\"rico\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M14 12h36v40H14z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M14 24h36M14 38h36M24 12v12M40 24v14\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/></svg></span><p>Este é só 1 capítulo — o livro <strong>inteiro</strong> em 1 resumo: cheat sheet + PDF no acervo &mdash; link na bio.</p></div><div class=\"row\"><span class=\"rico\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><circle cx=\"32\" cy=\"32\" r=\"22\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/><path d=\"M27 23l16 9-16 9z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><p>Prefere assistir? Resumo de ~5 min no <strong>YouTube</strong>.</p></div><div class=\"row\"><span class=\"rico\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M34 8L18 36h12l-4 20 20-30H34l4-18z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><p>Um grande livro destilado por semana. <strong>Siga @minutoreal1701</strong>.</p></div></div><div class=\"save\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M18 10h28v44L32 44 18 54z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg>Salve para revisar</div><div class=\"handle\">@minutoreal1701</div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i></div></div>"], "ch02-modelagem-shading": ["<div class=\"slide cover\"><div class=\"wordmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span><span class=\"name\">Minuto<b>Real</b></span></div><div class=\"kicker\">CAPÍTULO 2 DE 3</div><h1><span class=\"lt\">BLENDER</span> <span class=\"bd\">FUNDAMENTALS</span></h1><div class=\"author\">por Blender Foundation</div><div class=\"hook\"><span class=\"num\">3</span><span class=\"lbl\">ideias<br>que <span>ficam</span></span></div><div class=\"swipe\"><span>arrasta</span><span class=\"arrow\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M12 32h36M34 18l16 14-16 14\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"4\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide concept\"><div class=\"topbar\"><span class=\"brandmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span>Minuto<b>Real</b></span></div><div class=\"ed\"><div class=\"ed-head\"><div class=\"ed-num\">1</div><div class=\"ed-meta\"><div class=\"ed-kicker\">BLENDER FUNDAMENTALS</div><div class=\"ed-rule\"></div><div class=\"ed-source\">Capítulo 2 &middot; <b>Modelagem e Shading</b></div></div></div><h1 class=\"ed-title\">Ferramentas de mesh</h1><p class=\"ed-body\"><strong><span class=\"dc\">E</span>xtrude (E), Loop Cut (Ctrl+R), Bevel (Ctrl+B), Knife (K), Inset (I).</strong> Esse punhado de ferramentas resolve a maior parte da modelagem hard-surface que uma cena de produto precisa.</p><div class=\"ed-tip\"><span class=\"tipic\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M34 8L18 36h12l-4 20 20-30H34l4-18z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><div class=\"tiptext\"><div class=\"tiplabel\">Topologia limpa</div><div class=\"tipbody\">desde o início evita dor no shading e na animação.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide concept\"><div class=\"topbar\"><span class=\"brandmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span>Minuto<b>Real</b></span></div><div class=\"ed\"><div class=\"ed-head\"><div class=\"ed-num\">2</div><div class=\"ed-meta\"><div class=\"ed-kicker\">BLENDER FUNDAMENTALS</div><div class=\"ed-rule\"></div><div class=\"ed-source\">Capítulo 2 &middot; <b>Modelagem e Shading</b></div></div></div><h1 class=\"ed-title\">Principled BSDF (oficial)</h1><p class=\"ed-body\"><span class=\"dc\">O</span> shader padrão combina <strong>albedo, roughness, metalness e normal</strong> num nó só (modelo OpenPBR). É o caminho oficial p/ materiais realistas — domine-o antes de partir p/ nós complexos.</p><div class=\"ed-tip\"><span class=\"tipic\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M34 8L18 36h12l-4 20 20-30H34l4-18z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><div class=\"tiptext\"><div class=\"tiplabel\">Ordem</div><div class=\"tipbody\">Base Color → Roughness → Metallic; o resto é refino.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide concept\"><div class=\"topbar\"><span class=\"brandmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span>Minuto<b>Real</b></span></div><div class=\"ed\"><div class=\"ed-head\"><div class=\"ed-num\">3</div><div class=\"ed-meta\"><div class=\"ed-kicker\">BLENDER FUNDAMENTALS</div><div class=\"ed-rule\"></div><div class=\"ed-source\">Capítulo 2 &middot; <b>Modelagem e Shading</b></div></div></div><h1 class=\"ed-title\">UV antes de texturizar</h1><p class=\"ed-body\"><span class=\"dc\">O</span> fluxo oficial: <strong>marcar seams logicamente → Unwrap → compactar ilhas p/ minimizar distorção → só então texturizar.</strong> Pular o UV é a causa nº1 de textura esticada.</p><div class=\"ed-tip\"><span class=\"tipic\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M34 8L18 36h12l-4 20 20-30H34l4-18z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><div class=\"tiptext\"><div class=\"tiplabel\">Regra</div><div class=\"tipbody\">UV é parte da modelagem, não um detalhe do fim.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide lessons\"><div class=\"topbar\"><span class=\"brandmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span>Minuto<b>Real</b></span></div><div class=\"ed\"><div class=\"ed-head\"><div class=\"ed-num\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M18 10h28v44L32 44 18 54z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></div><div class=\"ed-meta\"><div class=\"ed-kicker\">BLENDERFUNDAMENTALS</div><div class=\"ed-rule\"></div><div class=\"ed-source\">Capítulo 2 &middot; <b>Modelagem e Shading</b></div></div></div><h1 class=\"ed-title\">Lições-Chave do Capítulo 2</h1><ul class=\"lessons-list\"><li><span class=\"lnum\">1</span>Um punhado de ferramentas (E/Ctrl+R/Ctrl+B/K/I) cobre a modelagem.</li><li><span class=\"lnum\">2</span>Principled BSDF é o caminho oficial para materiais PBR.</li><li><span class=\"lnum\">3</span>Faça o UV unwrap ANTES de texturizar.</li></ul></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide cta\"><div class=\"ghost\" style=\"bottom:150px;right:40px;font-size:300px\">+</div><div class=\"big\">Gostou?<br><span class=\"lt\">tem mais.</span></div><div class=\"rows\"><div class=\"row\"><span class=\"rico\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M14 12h36v40H14z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M14 24h36M14 38h36M24 12v12M40 24v14\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/></svg></span><p>Este é só 1 capítulo — o livro <strong>inteiro</strong> em 1 resumo: cheat sheet + PDF no acervo &mdash; link na bio.</p></div><div class=\"row\"><span class=\"rico\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><circle cx=\"32\" cy=\"32\" r=\"22\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/><path d=\"M27 23l16 9-16 9z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><p>Prefere assistir? Resumo de ~5 min no <strong>YouTube</strong>.</p></div><div class=\"row\"><span class=\"rico\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M34 8L18 36h12l-4 20 20-30H34l4-18z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><p>Um grande livro destilado por semana. <strong>Siga @minutoreal1701</strong>.</p></div></div><div class=\"save\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M18 10h28v44L32 44 18 54z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg>Salve para revisar</div><div class=\"handle\">@minutoreal1701</div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i></div></div>"], "ch03-luz-render-producao": ["<div class=\"slide cover\"><div class=\"wordmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span><span class=\"name\">Minuto<b>Real</b></span></div><div class=\"kicker\">CAPÍTULO 3 DE 3</div><h1><span class=\"lt\">BLENDER</span> <span class=\"bd\">FUNDAMENTALS</span></h1><div class=\"author\">por Blender Foundation</div><div class=\"hook\"><span class=\"num\">3</span><span class=\"lbl\">ideias<br>que <span>ficam</span></span></div><div class=\"swipe\"><span>arrasta</span><span class=\"arrow\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M12 32h36M34 18l16 14-16 14\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"4\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide concept\"><div class=\"topbar\"><span class=\"brandmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span>Minuto<b>Real</b></span></div><div class=\"ed\"><div class=\"ed-head\"><div class=\"ed-num\">1</div><div class=\"ed-meta\"><div class=\"ed-kicker\">BLENDER FUNDAMENTALS</div><div class=\"ed-rule\"></div><div class=\"ed-source\">Capítulo 3 &middot; <b>Luz, Render e Produção</b></div></div></div><h1 class=\"ed-title\">Iluminação de três pontos</h1><p class=\"ed-body\"><span class=\"dc\">A</span> técnica-base oficial: <strong>key (principal), fill (preenche a sombra) e rim (separa do fundo).</strong> Tipos de luz: Point, Sun, Spot, Area — a Area dá a sombra suave de estúdio.</p><div class=\"ed-tip\"><span class=\"tipic\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M34 8L18 36h12l-4 20 20-30H34l4-18z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><div class=\"tiptext\"><div class=\"tiplabel\">Comece pela key</div><div class=\"tipbody\">, depois alivie a sombra com o fill, por último separe com o rim.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide concept\"><div class=\"topbar\"><span class=\"brandmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span>Minuto<b>Real</b></span></div><div class=\"ed\"><div class=\"ed-head\"><div class=\"ed-num\">2</div><div class=\"ed-meta\"><div class=\"ed-kicker\">BLENDER FUNDAMENTALS</div><div class=\"ed-rule\"></div><div class=\"ed-source\">Capítulo 3 &middot; <b>Luz, Render e Produção</b></div></div></div><h1 class=\"ed-title\">Render + Denoising</h1><p class=\"ed-body\"><span class=\"dc\">N</span>o Cycles, <strong>ative sempre o Denoising</strong> p/ obter imagem limpa com menos samples — economiza muito tempo. Defina resolução e formato no painel de Output.</p><div class=\"ed-tip\"><span class=\"tipic\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M34 8L18 36h12l-4 20 20-30H34l4-18z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><div class=\"tiptext\"><div class=\"tiplabel\">Entrega</div><div class=\"tipbody\">EXR 32-bit p/ compositing; PNG p/ frames finais.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide concept\"><div class=\"topbar\"><span class=\"brandmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span>Minuto<b>Real</b></span></div><div class=\"ed\"><div class=\"ed-head\"><div class=\"ed-num\">3</div><div class=\"ed-meta\"><div class=\"ed-kicker\">BLENDER FUNDAMENTALS</div><div class=\"ed-rule\"></div><div class=\"ed-source\">Capítulo 3 &middot; <b>Luz, Render e Produção</b></div></div></div><h1 class=\"ed-title\">Compositor + Sequencer</h1><p class=\"ed-body\"><span class=\"dc\">O</span> Blender fecha o ciclo: <strong>o Compositor processa cada frame (cor, glare, grade) e o Video Sequencer monta o filme final com áudio</strong> — tudo sem sair do software.</p><div class=\"ed-tip\"><span class=\"tipic\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M34 8L18 36h12l-4 20 20-30H34l4-18z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><div class=\"tiptext\"><div class=\"tiplabel\">Prática oficial</div><div class=\"tipbody\">render → sequência de imagens → compositor → sequencer.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide lessons\"><div class=\"topbar\"><span class=\"brandmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span>Minuto<b>Real</b></span></div><div class=\"ed\"><div class=\"ed-head\"><div class=\"ed-num\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M18 10h28v44L32 44 18 54z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></div><div class=\"ed-meta\"><div class=\"ed-kicker\">BLENDERFUNDAMENTALS</div><div class=\"ed-rule\"></div><div class=\"ed-source\">Capítulo 3 &middot; <b>Luz, Render e Produção</b></div></div></div><h1 class=\"ed-title\">Lições-Chave do Capítulo 3</h1><ul class=\"lessons-list\"><li><span class=\"lnum\">1</span>Iluminação de três pontos (key/fill/rim) é a base oficial.</li><li><span class=\"lnum\">2</span>Ative Denoising no Cycles para limpar com menos samples.</li><li><span class=\"lnum\">3</span>Compositor (por frame) + Video Sequencer (montagem) fecham a produção.</li></ul></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide cta\"><div class=\"ghost\" style=\"bottom:150px;right:40px;font-size:300px\">+</div><div class=\"big\">Gostou?<br><span class=\"lt\">tem mais.</span></div><div class=\"rows\"><div class=\"row\"><span class=\"rico\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M14 12h36v40H14z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M14 24h36M14 38h36M24 12v12M40 24v14\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/></svg></span><p>Este é só 1 capítulo — o livro <strong>inteiro</strong> em 1 resumo: cheat sheet + PDF no acervo &mdash; link na bio.</p></div><div class=\"row\"><span class=\"rico\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><circle cx=\"32\" cy=\"32\" r=\"22\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/><path d=\"M27 23l16 9-16 9z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><p>Prefere assistir? Resumo de ~5 min no <strong>YouTube</strong>.</p></div><div class=\"row\"><span class=\"rico\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M34 8L18 36h12l-4 20 20-30H34l4-18z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><p>Um grande livro destilado por semana. <strong>Siga @minutoreal1701</strong>.</p></div></div><div class=\"save\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M18 10h28v44L32 44 18 54z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg>Salve para revisar</div><div class=\"handle\">@minutoreal1701</div>